SBAC Privacy Policy

1. Information We Collect
SBAC may collect:

User IDs (Roblox username or ID)

In-game actions, telemetry, and behavioral data related strictly to cheat detection

2. How We Use Information
We use data solely to detect and prevent cheating within supported Roblox games. We do not sell or share this data with third parties.

3. Data Storage and Security
All collected data is securely stored. We implement reasonable security measures (e.g., encryption, restricted access) to protect data.

4. Data Retention
We retain anti-cheat data only as long as necessary for cheat detection and audit purposes.

5. User Rights
Users may request deletion of personal data by contacting us at discord.gg/RQ7exsTcwK.

6. Changes to Policy
We may update this policy. Continued use means acceptance of any changes.

7. Contact
Questions: spidr@spidrbot.com
